Describes a reasoning framework, i.e., gives meta information that is associated with an RF. This is not a fact in the fact base. It comes from the RF configuration file.

Property paramTypes is used internally by SEI.ArchE.Configurator. SEI.ArchE.UI should use property respParamTypes to obtain the parameter types of responsibilities in that RF.
